OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fwill fade leaving a dry and mostly
OL,7,Fclear night to come. Some patchy cloud
OL,8,Fbut light winds expected. A cooler
OL,9,Fnight than of later, slightly in the
OL,10,Fsouthwest.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FPatchy cloud to start across
OL,13,Fthe midlands. This lifts to a bright
OL,14,Fand sunny Sunday. Isolated showers in
OL,15,FCornwall and northern Scotland where
OL,16,Fit'll be cloudier. Staying warm for
OL,17,Fmost.
